\c 24
\s UJesu ukhuluma ngokuchithwa kweJerusalema langokuphela kwesikhathi
\p
\v 1 UJesu wasephuma\x + Mark. 13.1-37. Luka 21.5-36.\x* wasuka ethempelini\x + 21.23.\x*; basebesondela abafundi bakhe ukumtshengisa izakhiwo zethempeli.
\v 2 UJesu wasesithi kubo: Kaliziboni yini zonke lezizinto? Ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Akusoze kutshiywe lapha ilitshe elilodwa phezu kwelitshe, elingasoze lidilizelwe phansi\x + Luka 19.44. 1 Kho. 9.7. Jer. 26.18. Mika 3.12.\x*.
\p
\v 3 Kwathi esehlezi entabeni yeMihlwathi\x + 21.1.\x*, abafundi beza kuye bebodwa, bathi: Sitshele, lezizinto zizakuba nini\x + Mark. 13.3.\x*? Lesibonakaliso sokuza kwakho, lesokuphela kwesikhathi \add sizakuba\add* yini\x + 13.39.\x*?
\p
\v 4 UJesu wasephendula wathi kubo: Qaphelani, kungabi khona oliduhisayo\x + Jer. 29.8. Efe. 5.6. Kol. 2.8. 2 Thes. 2.3.\x*;
