\v 6 Njalo lizakuzwa ngezimpi lamahungahunga ezimpi; nanzelelani, lingethuki; ngoba konke \add lokhu\add* kufanele kwenzeke; kodwa ukuphela kakukabi khona\x + 2 Thes. 2.2.\x*.
\v 7 Ngoba isizwe sizavukela isizwe\x + 2 Lan. 15.6.\x*, lombuso u\add vuk\add*ele umbuso\x + Isa. 19.2. Jer. 51.46. Hag. 2.22. Zek. 14.13.\x*; njalo kuzakuba khona indlala labomatshayabhuqe bezifo lokuzamazama komhlaba indawo ngendawo\x + Seb. 11.28.\x*;
