\v 9 Lapho-ke bazalinikela\x + 10.17,21. Joha. 15.20; 16.2. 1 Pet. 4.16. Luka 21.12.\x* ekuhluphekeni, balibulale; futhi lizazondwa yizizwe zonke ngenxa yebizo lami\x + Isam. 2.10.\x*.
\v 10 Njalo ngalesosikhathi abanengi bazakhubeka\x + 11.6. 2 Tim. 1.15; 4.10,16.\x*, banikelane, bazondane.
\v 11 Futhi kuzavuka abaprofethi bamanga abanengi\x + 7.15. 1 Tim. 4.1.\x*, baduhise abanengi\x + 24.5,24.\x*.
\v 12 Njalo ngenxa yokwanda kobubi, uthando lwabanengi luzaphola;
