\v 14 Njalo lelivangeli lombuso\x + 4.23.\x* lizatshunyayelwa\x + Roma 10.18 Kol. 1.6,23. 2 Tim. 4.17.\x* emhlabeni wonke\x + Luka 2.1; 4.5; 21.26. Seb. 11.28; 17.6,31; 19.27; 24.5. Roma 10.18. Heb. 1.6; 2.5. Isam. 3.10; 12.9; 16.14.\x* kube yibufakazi ezizweni zonke; khona-ke kuzafika ukuphela\x + 8.4.\x*.
