\v 15 Ngakho nxa libona amanyala encithakalo, akhulunywa nguDaniyeli umprofethi\x + Dan. 9.27. 11.31; 12.11.\x*, emi endaweni engcwele\x + Seb. 6.13. Mark. 13.14.\x* (obalayo kaqedisise)\x + Dan. 9.23,25.\x*,
\v 16 khona labo abaseJudiya kababalekele ezintabeni;
