\v 22 Uba-ke lezonsuku bezingafinyezwanga, bekungesindiswe nyama\x + Luka 21.22.\x*; kodwa ngenxa yabakhethiweyo lezonsuku zizafinyezwa\x + 24.24,31. Isa. 65.8,9,15,22.\x*.
