\v 23 Ngalesosikhathi nxa umuntu esithi kini: Khangelani, nangu uKristu, kumbe nanguya, lingakholwa\x + Luka 17.23.\x*.
\v 24 Ngoba kuzavuka okristu bamanga labaprofethi bamanga\x + 24.5,11. 7.15.\x*, benze izibonakaliso ezinkulu lezimangaliso\x + Dute. 13.1-3. 2 Thes. 2.9-11. Isam. 13.13,14; 16.14.\x*, ukuze kuthi, nxa kungenzeka, baduhise labakhethiweyo\x + 24.24,31. Isa. 65.8,9,15,22.\x*.
\v 25 Khangelani, sengilitshelile ngaphambili.
\v 26 Ngakho uba bengathi kini\x + Luka 12.20.\x*: Khangelani, usenkangala, lingaphumi; khangelani, \add us\add*endlini yensitha, lingakholwa\x + Seb. 21.28.\x*.
\v 27 Ngoba njengalokhu umbane ubaneka empumalanga ukhanye lentshonalanga, kuzakuba njalo lokufika kweNdodana yomuntu\x + Luka 17.24.\x*.
