\v 29 Njalo masinyane emva kokuhlupheka kwalezonsuku\x + 24.21.\x*, ilanga lizafiphazwa, lenyanga kayiyikupha ukukhanya kwayo\x + Isa. 13.10; 24.23. Hez. 32.7. Jow. 2.10,31; 3.15. Amos 5.20; 8.9. Zef. 1.15. Seb. 2.20. Isam. 6.12.\x*, lenkanyezi zizakuwa ezulwini, lamandla amazulu azazanyazanyiswa\x + Isam. 6.13. 2 Pet. 3.10,12.\x*.
\v 30 Khona-ke sizabonakala\x + Dan. 7.13.\x* ezulwini isibonakaliso seNdodana yomuntu\x + 24.3.\x*; njalo besezikhala zonke izizwe zomhlaba\x + Isam. 1.7.\x*, sezibona\x + Zek. 12.12.\x* iNdodana yomuntu\x + 16.27.\x* isiza emayezini ezulu\x + Isam. 1.7.\x* ilamandla lenkazimulo enkulu\x + Mark. 9.1.\x*.
