\v 32 Kodwa fundani umfanekiso emkhiweni; nxa khathesi ugatsha lwawo selusiba buthakathaka, njalo luhlume amahlamvu, liyazi ukuthi ihlobo seliseduze;
\v 33 ngokunjalo lani, nxa libona lezizinto zonke, yazini ukuthi kuseduze\f + \fk kuseduze: \ft kumbe, \fq useduze\f* kuseminyango\x + Jak. 5.9.\x*.
\v 34 Ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Lesisizukulwana asisoze sidlule, kuze kwenzeke zonke lezizinto\x + 16.28.\x*.
\v 35 Kuzadlula izulu lomhlaba\x + Hlab. 102.26. Isa. 51.6. Jer. 31.35,36. Mat. 5.18. Heb. 1.11.\x*, kodwa amazwi ami awasoze adlule\x + Hlab. 119.89. Isa. 40.8.\x*.
