\v 42 Ngakho lindani\x + 24.43.25.13; 26 38,40,41. Mark. 13.34,35,37; 14.34,37,38. Luka 12.37,39. Seb. 20.31. 1 Kor. 16.13. Kol. 4.2. 1 Thes. 5.6,10. 1 Pet. 5.8. Isam. 3.2,3; 16.15.\x*, ngoba kalazi ukuthi iNkosi yenu izafika ngaliphi ihola\x + 24.36.25.13. Luka 12.40.\x*.
